  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"2.5.0-alpha03\" data-text=\"Version 2.5.0-alpha03\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 2.5.0-alpha03</h3>\n<p>May 29, 2024</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.sqlite:sqlite-*:2.5.0-alpha03</code> is released. Version 2.5.0-alpha03 contains <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/6a69101fd0edc8d02aa316df1f43e0552fd2d7c4..473554f275109d78164adca6b6cea539aed8b68b/sqlite\">these commits</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix an issue with the <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">BundledSQLiteDriver</code> where databases created with it would contain the C null terminator character. (<a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/314151707\">b/340822359</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
